name: auth_user
schema:
CREATE TABLE [auth_user] (
   [id] INTEGER PRIMARY KEY,
   [password] TEXT,
   [last_login] TEXT,
   [is_superuser] INTEGER,
   [username] TEXT,
   [first_name] TEXT,
   [last_name] TEXT,
   [email] TEXT,
   [is_staff] INTEGER,
   [is_active] INTEGER,
   [date_joined] TEXT
)
